Author: EzraCelestine
Text: Had the same experience when I started squel. In my experience it hasn't been a *temporary* side effect as much as it's just become a lot easier to manage. Like, it sorta becomes your new baseline and while that's obvi not enjoyable it basically just becomes a slightly hungrier version of the you you were before, but it doesn't take more effort than pre-med you did once you're used to it
